{
  "texts": [
    "Recapti [26] harnessed the power of Large Language Models (LLM) to improve the text comprehension capabilities of LDM, enabling training-free T2I generation.",
    "Furthermore, the integration of additional control signals [27]- [31] has further expanded the applicability of Diffusion Models in T2I generation.",
    "Unlike image generation, the task of video generation required by MagicTime is more complex, as it necessitates both diversity in content across space and consistency in content across time.",
    "Text-to-Video GenerationThe advent of large-scale video-text datasets [32]- [34] has facilitated significant advancements in pre-trained video diffusion models [5], [6], [35]- [42].",
    "MagicVideo2 [43] utilized cascaded diffusion to separate image and video generation, starting with text to initially generate images and subsequently produce highquality videos."
  ]
}